WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: fr

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Transcription: Clara Nathan
Relecteur: eric vautier

00:00:12.180 --> 00:00:30.510
(Musique)

00:00:30.510 --> 00:00:34.180
La peinture plein les doigts,

00:00:34.180 --> 00:00:38.180
je refais cent fois

00:00:38.180 --> 00:00:43.300
le chemin à l'envers

00:00:43.300 --> 00:00:49.380
de ce qu'il reste à défaire.

00:00:49.380 --> 00:00:52.970
Ces empreintes d'autrefois,

00:00:52.970 --> 00:00:57.030
ces murmures en moi,

00:00:57.030 --> 00:01:02.150
j'apprends du mur son repère

00:01:02.150 --> 00:01:07.604
et ça commence à me plaire.

00:01:07.604 --> 00:01:12.644
Tu murmures, me rassures,

00:01:12.644 --> 00:01:16.924
apaises les blessures,

00:01:16.924 --> 00:01:21.804
du zeste à l'azur,

00:01:21.804 --> 00:01:27.504
du reste, j'en suis sûre.

00:01:27.504 --> 00:01:31.584
Et j'efface les ratures

00:01:31.584 --> 00:01:35.408
du bout des doigts.

00:01:35.408 --> 00:01:40.752
Les mots me viennent, je les perds

00:01:40.752 --> 00:01:46.992
quand la magie opère.

00:01:46.992 --> 00:01:50.802
A l'abri dans ma bulle,

00:01:50.802 --> 00:01:55.002
je répète cent fois,

00:01:55.002 --> 00:02:00.552
les prières de fortune

00:02:00.552 --> 00:02:05.812
qui m'ont menée à toi.

00:02:05.812 --> 00:02:10.792
Tu murmures, me rassures,

00:02:10.792 --> 00:02:15.522
apaises mes blessures,

00:02:15.522 --> 00:02:20.772
du zeste à l'azur,

00:02:20.772 --> 00:02:25.394
du reste, j'en suis sûre.

00:02:25.394 --> 00:02:30.604
Oh, enlève ton armure.

00:02:30.604 --> 00:02:35.534
Pourquoi c'est si dur ?

00:02:35.534 --> 00:02:40.734
Oh d'un geste, à l'armure,

00:02:40.734 --> 00:02:48.874
du reste, j'en suis sûre.

00:02:48.874 --> 00:03:00.144
(Applaudissements)

00:03:00.144 --> 00:03:01.837
On m'a dit « interlude ».

00:03:01.837 --> 00:03:03.977
On m'a dit :
« Tu vas voir, les gens d'Annecy,

00:03:03.977 --> 00:03:07.007
ils chantent super bien. »

00:03:07.007 --> 00:03:08.977
Du coup, je me suis dit,

00:03:08.977 --> 00:03:11.507
comme un peu tous les intervenants ici,

00:03:11.507 --> 00:03:14.377
le tout, ce n'est pas forcément
de dire les choses,

00:03:14.377 --> 00:03:16.937
c'est de les faire.

00:03:16.937 --> 00:03:19.147
Alors comme moi, je vous aime, et ben,

00:03:19.147 --> 00:03:21.777
je vous ai écrit une chanson d'amour

00:03:21.777 --> 00:03:25.487
et ça va être facile à la fin en fait,

00:03:25.487 --> 00:03:27.527
peut-être, si vous avez envie,

00:03:27.527 --> 00:03:30.437
vous allez pouvoir
répéter le refrain avec moi,

00:03:30.437 --> 00:03:34.517
et ça dit juste « Love » et « Song ».

00:03:34.517 --> 00:03:36.147
Il y a des petits mots

00:03:36.147 --> 00:03:37.557
mais c'est assez simple.

00:03:37.557 --> 00:03:38.607
C'est en anglais,

00:03:38.607 --> 00:03:42.237
comme ça personne pourra voir si
vous ne dites pas les vrais mots, tout ça.

00:03:42.237 --> 00:03:42.967
(Rires)

00:03:42.967 --> 00:03:44.357
Elle fait comme ça.

00:03:44.357 --> 00:04:00.627
(Musique)

00:04:00.627 --> 00:04:04.287
Here is my love song,

00:04:04.287 --> 00:04:07.477
the one I never wrote to you.

00:04:07.477 --> 00:04:14.217
I gotta do this on my own, not forget you.

00:04:14.217 --> 00:04:17.837
Here is my love song,

00:04:17.837 --> 00:04:21.029
simply words melody to

00:04:21.029 --> 00:04:24.939
something like my only way.

00:04:24.939 --> 00:04:29.029
To remember you, we're at this for.

00:04:29.029 --> 00:04:30.619
We've seen us growing

00:04:30.619 --> 00:04:36.879
strongly snuggling for what it's worth,

00:04:36.879 --> 00:04:40.419
for what it's worth.

00:04:40.419 --> 00:04:43.759
Even into deep, we won't let go.

00:04:43.759 --> 00:04:47.429
Time doesn't it always flee ?

00:04:47.429 --> 00:04:53.704
But I love you so, I love you so.

00:04:53.704 --> 00:05:01.724
Here is my love song, my love song,

00:05:01.724 --> 00:05:07.824
my love song to you.

00:05:07.824 --> 00:05:14.684
Here is my love song, my love song

00:05:14.684 --> 00:05:23.384
my love song to you.

00:05:23.384 --> 00:05:26.894
Here is my love song

00:05:26.894 --> 00:05:30.744
when the sun went up I have no word.

00:05:30.744 --> 00:05:33.919
Out threw love new emotions

00:05:33.919 --> 00:05:37.094
but I'm not sure.

00:05:37.094 --> 00:05:40.874
Here is my love song.

00:05:40.874 --> 00:05:44.924
Have to sing it before the night goes away

00:05:44.924 --> 00:05:47.954
- don't get me wrong.

00:05:47.954 --> 00:05:49.464
I'm gonna miss you,

00:05:49.464 --> 00:05:51.034
we're at this for.

00:05:51.034 --> 00:05:55.484
We've seen us growing strongly snuggling

00:05:55.484 --> 00:06:02.854
for what it's worth, for what it's worth.

00:06:02.854 --> 00:06:06.234
Even into deep, we won't let go.

00:06:06.234 --> 00:06:09.704
Time doesn't it always flee ?

00:06:09.704 --> 00:06:15.724
I love you so, I love you so.

00:06:15.724 --> 00:06:23.274
Here is my love song, my love song,

00:06:23.274 --> 00:06:29.604
my love song to you.

00:06:29.604 --> 00:06:36.150
Here is my love song, my love song,

00:06:36.150 --> 00:06:41.270
my love song to you.

00:06:41.270 --> 00:06:42.640
And sing :

00:06:42.640 --> 00:06:49.020
Here is my love song, my love song,

00:06:49.020 --> 00:06:54.930
my love song to you.

00:06:54.930 --> 00:06:56.100
Encore !

00:06:56.100 --> 00:07:02.507
Here is my love song, my love song,

00:07:02.507 --> 00:07:07.417
my love song to you.

00:07:07.417 --> 00:07:09.007
Encore !

00:07:09.007 --> 00:07:15.737
Here is my love song, my love song,

00:07:15.737 --> 00:07:22.857
my love song to you.

00:07:22.857 --> 00:07:25.137
To you.

00:07:25.137 --> 00:07:33.033
